  N2 --> N3{PB: Process Builder - Develop contingency plans and identify alternate sources.}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[Cortex: RCA Service - Monitor supplier financial health and trigger alerts.]
  N4 --> N5[PB: CWB Lifecycle - Present recommendations for supplier actions to stakeholders.]
  N5 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced working capital tied to safety stock and lead-time risks, improved OTIF, and enhanced supplier resilience.]
  N3 -->|High risk detected in supplier financ...| B1[Initiate supplier diversification or renegotiation process.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Improved supplier resilience and reduced financial risk.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Potential material shortage identified.| B2[Expedite orders or adjust safety stock levels.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Minimized impact of supply disruptions.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|No single points of failure identified.| B3[Continue monitoring and regular assessments.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Maintained supply chain visibility and resilience.]
  O3 --> End[End]
